{"tid":2034260,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"遊記 2019長野避暑之旅","createTime":"2020-05-25T06:43:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T17:55:27.000Z","uid":310755,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d696e0fbfc9dd10e61d9c337433a491d16ab891d","tid":2034260,"uid":310755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T06:43:03.000Z","msg":"入正題之前，先悼念一下因為甴大大搞到咁而去唔成既「2020山陰&amp;關西之旅」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LA15OOX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLA15OOX.png&h=1d9c7789&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n是咁的，小弟就普通毒撚一個，去親旅行都係孤獨一人，不過，亦都有好處，唔洗同人夾行程又唔洗遷就人，都咪話唔過癮<br />\n<br />\n行程方面我就通常一日一個景點算喇，去旅行都係為左放鬆一下，又何必趕頭趕命<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁個避暑之旅就總共九日，八晚換過四間酒店<br />\n<br />\n行程<br />\n<br />\nDay1 NH822羽田機場-&gt;新宿-&gt;茅野-&gt;蓼科<br />\n<br />\nDay2 茅野-&gt;松本-&gt;大王農場<br />\n<br />\nDay3 上高地<br />\n<br />\nDay4 松本-&gt;善光寺-&gt;輕井澤<br />\n<br />\nDay5 舊輕井澤<br />\n<br />\nDay6-9 東京"},{"pid":"32c59ccb296fc17d7eff904ad9b1a01677506663","tid":2034260,"uid":310755,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T07:10:04.000Z","msg":"Day1-1<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去東京既首選當然係全日空NH822紅眼航班，可惜已經冇左，從此以後想紅眼飛羽田就得返UO<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/05/25/144649_2b732959027a3618feb75d1fcd1c19e6.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F05%2F25%2F144649_2b732959027a3618feb75d1fcd1c19e6.jpeg&h=8e8012ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nANA三等人倉飛機餐，主菜係雞肉&amp;薯蓉，再配生果沙律同冷麵三個小食<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6JMUHoC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6JMUHoC.jpg&h=8ff84700&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本來係想食完野瞓一陣，可惜都係瞓唔着，索性派第二round野飲時問空姐要一杯咖啡好過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就係咁眼光光等天光終於到左羽田機場<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZcUryxV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZcUryxV.jpg&h=c343e0be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPS:丫邊個仆街同我講飛羽田有機見到富士山既呢，等我劃左手邊窗口位點知睇左成朝雲"},{"pid":"7da8d82b6c5336e28970a1c314be89091f3c6c4d","tid":2034260,"uid":310755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T10:45:25.000Z","msg":"清晨六點到羽田，等入境，等行李，排綠色窗口拎pass,搞得黎坐monorail入城已經係八點既事<br />\n<br />\n話說如果行程比較緊既話寧可花少少錢坐京急出品川再搞pass好過，羽田個綠色窗口好多人排，我行程唔趕先同佢慢慢等<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拎pass順便book第一程既特急<br />\n1pm新宿出發既Asuza17，茅野落車，車程大約兩個鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktPZUJd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktPZUJd.jpg&h=0a5ca376&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拎左pass就去坐mono去濱松町，大鄉里第一次坐東京單軌，之前兩次飛羽田因爲冇買pass關係都係坐京急<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2JyjUJv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2JyjUJv.jpg&h=edf2ea17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐monorail出濱松町轉山手線，唔洗一陣就到左新宿，仲有成四個鐘多d先坐火車出城，先搵locker放低件行李再搵地方打發時間<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EjmNjaz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEjmNjaz.jpg&h=26864235&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"864f107be37b90351d8b73046159380275f44c1c","tid":2034260,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T12:11:19.000Z","msg":"毒遊最正"},{"pid":"befafd50d116daeda3698ae3d2f377ee10f5dbd0","tid":2034260,"uid":8934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T16:23:43.000Z","msg":"上高地正"},{"pid":"4934558f7725d605ec5391d340c2347cfaf3b415","tid":2034260,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T18:10:21.000Z","msg":"爛左？"},{"pid":"68c09f2ddc4dc3cff7caf9cc44ed6eef4cec2691","tid":2034260,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T23:23:16.000Z","msg":"，lm"},{"pid":"373c5479041ecfdb47e9b54cb32a613b54578bf2","tid":2034260,"uid":310755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4934558f7725d605ec5391d340c2347cfaf3b415","tid":2034260,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T18:10:21.000Z","msg":"爛左？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T03:11:06.000Z","msg":"冇爛"},{"pid":"4a6a4ce79bf8d0d0430d2d1a570bb11ff25f521a","tid":2034260,"uid":310755,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T03:36:25.000Z","msg":"朝早，九點新宿，晨早流流都唔知做乜好，仲要搵地方鳩到一點坐火車，身為毒撚唔通去無料案內所咩，咁想蒲下機鋪但係人地開十點正<br />\n<br />\n於是先去食個早餐，近近地去果實園食個生果三文治<br />\n<br />\nPS:呢間野早餐時間入面全部客都係架妹，冇仔，利申冇圖<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/05/26/111743_890d45cb8aed0ea49b25e69c7a2ea9b0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F05%2F26%2F111743_890d45cb8aed0ea49b25e69c7a2ea9b0.jpeg&h=aa6222db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完個早餐終於等到十點機鋪開門，打幾鋪機打發下時間<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yHOTkg9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyHOTkg9.jpg&h=f71e6780&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uDZfyCa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuDZfyCa.png&h=a4f44570&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n丫冇訓成晚又算打得幾好<br />\n打完四局都差不多十一點<br />\n係時候諗下lunch食乜<br />\n<br />\n打機個名叫敘敘苑咁就一於去食敘敘苑<br />\n意思意思叫個lunch set B<br />\n毒撚要求唔高，敘敘苑lunch夠用㗎啦，真係好撚正<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bk7kKLq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBk7kKLq.jpg&h=3111b1c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飲飽食醉就慢慢行返去jr 站拎行李搭火車<br />\n今日既交通工具，E353系，冇左super字頭既asuza <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FwvuC6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFwvuC6c.jpg&h=19820a45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開始出發去茅野，既然係「茅野」就梗係要同老婆自拍返張<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NT1qbsj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNT1qbsj.jpg&h=fb982b38&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60ab5ed7f1077800e6a3386d0171f9f329ab1495","tid":2034260,"uid":310755,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:47:03.000Z","msg":"本來plan行程時仲打算中途係小淵澤落車去睇白州蒸餾所，可惜呢日既參觀名額已經full左，只好下次再去<br />\n<br />\n半訓半醒咁叫做訓左兩個鐘，好快就到左茅野站，已經入左長野縣，正式開始呢個長野既旅程<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RRV6Hoo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRRV6Hoo.jpg&h=eee8fc57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n落左車就係等温泉旅館既shuttle，然後上蓼科溫泉<br />\n<br />\n今晚住既係「蓼科 親湯溫泉」，八疊和室一泊兩食盛惠13365羊（連稅）<br />\n<br />\n點解揀呢度呢，其實都只係係relux上面睇到價錢丶評分都唔錯，又算係順路，就book左佢<br />\n<br />\n落車既時候落住雨所以都冇影溫泉旅館既正面，啱啱renew左冇耐，內裡d裝修幾唔錯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yPLynoG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyPLynoG.jpg&h=c7a7e8e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eF5Obhh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeF5Obhh.jpg&h=b835fb28&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z4tzRhn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ4tzRhn.jpg&h=c3b855db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今晚訓既地方，八疊和室一間，for一條友乜都夠喇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZMJLXXA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZMJLXXA.jpg&h=da5b6713&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/05/26/174430_05d50e4751dd44df7998b06aaee2d018.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F05%2F26%2F174430_05d50e4751dd44df7998b06aaee2d018.jpeg&h=fad78f2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天氣麻麻，乜鳩都睇唔到，都係換浴衣去浸溫泉算<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0fprHpS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0fprHpS.jpg&h=741def8d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/46h8VK3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F46h8VK3.jpg&h=1f20c261&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大浴場唔比影相，用官網相頂住先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O0Dj2pA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO0Dj2pA.png&h=c0fb037e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oPzLdwg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoPzLdwg.png&h=7f2ff161&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n浸左一round舒服晒，疲勞盡消，行到返大廳鬼影都冇隻，似乎係時候食晚飯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請問呢碟係咩黎嫁？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JKNH0bT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJKNH0bT.jpg&h=e2a7fdd8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c902e3131935157fb69a5eb9d08d541292b47754","tid":2034260,"uid":100131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:31:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />飛羽田真係見到富士山，我都係睇網上教坐左邊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BYN8XFc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBYN8XFc.jpg&h=69a26fc3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36594b5aacc537296baa567ef108318f5e06d23e","tid":2034260,"uid":134182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:12:58.000Z","msg":"留名睇文"},{"pid":"e5d6cb5b02d978b3499c6439184576236c6a782d","tid":2034260,"uid":55232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T07:16:59.000Z","msg":"LM folllow"},{"pid":"e55fe13fc5b8eef9d64a28b6d2b12ab33b45fb4b","tid":2034260,"uid":310755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T09:43:10.000Z","msg":"個晚餐由一開始就有d唔對路，餐廳門口係一個金髮鬼妹侍應接待，然後帶位係個鬼仔侍應<br />\n<br />\n我去左一個叫茅野既鄉下地方，離開東京兩個半鐘車程，呢度唔會有好多外國遊客掛，點解呢度咁多洋鬼子員工<br />\n<br />\n望住個頭盤真係打左個突，做乜溫泉旅館既晚餐係法國菜，乜去溫泉一泊兩食個晚餐唔係都係會席料理擺到成抬九大簋咁嫁咩<br />\n<br />\n拎起個餐牌睇，點睇都係法國菜<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C0gqmdk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC0gqmdk.jpg&h=a46e60ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n丫但係味道又真係幾好，三扒兩撥就食曬個小食拼盤<br />\n<br />\n然後上佢餐牌所寫嘅鴨皮太沙（appetizer)，係一粒蕃茄，真係越黎越古怪<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/05/27/171313_77a8718a77d1288536244ca167c5cd37.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F05%2F27%2F171313_77a8718a77d1288536244ca167c5cd37.jpeg&h=0b8988da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n栗米湯，好甜，好日本人口味<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1oW55Nz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1oW55Nz.jpg&h=fe20561d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n既然係法國大餐咁有舊魚都好應該<br />\n石班伴香醋汁，我唔好海鮮所以冇評論<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3aO8i8D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3aO8i8D.jpg&h=94fed5d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n牛，好似係當地名產黎，配佢個山葵醬好好食<br />\n大概係用左真山葵而唔是牙膏支裝「山葵」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MQmYGoJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMQmYGoJ.jpg&h=850edf48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好水下既湯咖哩，一開頭以為會好淡，出奇地濃味同辣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5figs4z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5figs4z.jpg&h=4bfa6cbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n甜品冇咩特別好講，好甜好日本口味<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U2D0UK9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU2D0UK9.jpg&h=1344165f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有啲出乎意料之外但仍然係好食嘅一餐"},{"pid":"4c83cbc7f0e0e7e5f18ae7ee5d630ced7bfa4a63","tid":2034260,"uid":310755,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T17:14:41.000Z","msg":"食飽之後抖左陣又去浸溫泉，個plan包左半個鐘一節既私人風呂，咁就當然要用埋佢<br />\ncheckin 時已經book左時段，去reception同佢講用私人風呂就會有人帶路<br />\n<br />\n又係果個金髮鬼妹侍應，可惜我就毒撚一個都唔知點樣同人搭訕好，但係行到一半佢居然開口問我&rdquo;where did you coming from&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n咁我答完佢「香港」之後就順便問返佢邊樹人啦，答案都有d離奇，居然係露西亞<br />\n起立唱番首國歌先<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AOAtz8xWM0w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAOAtz8xWM0w&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3oVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=3c051fdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AOAtz8xWM0w</a><br />\n<br />\n俄國人喎，煙文我就得姐，俄文咪只係識得係CSGO學返嚟既Cyka 同 Blyat，絕對唔係適合同女性講嘅單詞<br />\n好彩睇得meme多，記得一首洗腦歌個開頭，於是就同佢講我識唱首俄文歌，佢既反應就係一個ORLY<br />\n<br />\n於是我仲真係開始左唱<br />\n&ldquo;Ka~lin ka~ka~lin ka~ka~lin ka~mo~ya&rdquo;<br />\n係&rdquo;Kalinka&rdquo;，著名俄國民歌，照計冇俄國人唔懂掛，丫我唱到一半佢仲真係跟我唱喎<br />\n<br />\n打咗咁大段嘢如果仲係txt應該會俾人屌<br />\n金髮俄妹示意圖，from溫泉官網<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GVZWvF5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGVZWvF5.png&h=b903a1da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n件事仲真係有啲超現實，去到日本旅行係一個荒山野嶺食法國菜以及同俄妹唱歌<br />\n可惜快樂嘅時光總係短暫嘅，好快就行到去私人風呂嘅門口，佢就面帶微笑交低條匙俾我就走左去<br />\n<br />\n老實講一條友都幾悶下，真係得個浸字<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pKSEtp6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpKSEtp6.jpg&h=45cca809&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n半個鐘之後返到去lobby交返條匙已經見唔番俄妹小姐，到最後都冇問人拎contact呀屌，只好返房訓<br />\n<br />\n就係咁第一晚結束左"},{"pid":"16bf48e97f489158ee3bab9c9b1f56035a1c5e8c","tid":2034260,"uid":210682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:35:15.000Z","msg":"正啊ANA，佢有winglet嘅763都唔算舊"},{"pid":"28bd383c9818268f6cd1ceb2cde7a01f80d882d9","tid":2034260,"uid":310755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T17:12:08.000Z","msg":"紅眼班機訓唔到既關係呢覺好好訓<br />\n<br />\n起身食早餐，終於係正常好多既日式早餐<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UbAKLdu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUbAKLdu.jpg&h=a7afb37b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知係唔係廚房出唔切，六個前菜分兩次上<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aa9PbTB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faa9PbTB.jpg&h=f723094a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0L0R9Fk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0L0R9Fk.jpg&h=594be54f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食飽就check out走人，可惜都係見唔到俄妹小姐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n坐温泉提供既接駁車返到落茅野站，然後就係等火車上松本<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7LvCkPm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7LvCkPm.jpg&h=28f4229d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TJWNK5s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTJWNK5s.jpg&h=00356900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMatsumoto~Matsumoto~<br />\n<br />\n號稱樂都丶岳都丶學都既松本，最出名既就莫過於松本城同上高地<br />\n松本城上次已經去過，今次黎松本既目的自然係上高地<br />\n不過火車到站已經十一點幾，去上高地有d遲，明天再戰，先去酒店寄存行李<br />\n<br />\n住既係松本Buena Vista酒店，離松本站五分鐘路程，單人房(17平方米）5800羊一晚唔包早餐<br />\n<br />\n有排都未到三點checkin，所以放低左行李就行返去jr站開始今日既行程，其實呢日冇乜特別，近近去睇下大王山葵農場食個wasabi雪糕打發下時間算<br />\n<br />\n大王？你哋有冇聽過大王個名呀？<br />\n<br />\n首先坐jr去穗高<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MuwYRXT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMuwYRXT.jpg&h=f2003f18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n問題係jr站去農場既巴士班次非常少，而我要係穗高等成個鐘先有下一班車，與其喺度白等不如行過去算<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ySYsLjz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FySYsLjz.png&h=6e139e5f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9793fe5c42385c91b3786f31b112504e08a78e9","tid":2034260,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"befafd50d116daeda3698ae3d2f377ee10f5dbd0","tid":2034260,"uid":8934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T16:23:43.000Z","msg":"上高地正"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:57:14.000Z","msg":"留一晚仲好"},{"pid":"c54362552327b5afccfc477e6d0e3ee3c00a6355","tid":2034260,"uid":310755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9793fe5c42385c91b3786f31b112504e08a78e9","tid":2034260,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"befafd50d116daeda3698ae3d2f377ee10f5dbd0","tid":2034260,"uid":8934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T16:23:43.000Z","msg":"上高地正"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:57:14.000Z","msg":"留一晚仲好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T01:46:55.000Z","msg":"冇女又冇錢唔留啦"},{"pid":"f4efa3246cf55d59d2aea14d28bab493a66ee2e2","tid":2034260,"uid":8934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9793fe5c42385c91b3786f31b112504e08a78e9","tid":2034260,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"befafd50d116daeda3698ae3d2f377ee10f5dbd0","tid":2034260,"uid":8934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T16:23:43.000Z","msg":"上高地正"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:57:14.000Z","msg":"留一晚仲好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T02:10:31.000Z","msg":"貴:("},{"pid":"71d8fc5618b0205f375e2128893376b6a5e7d2fd","tid":2034260,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T07:00:11.000Z","msg":"樓主冇邀請鬼妹一齊浸？"},{"pid":"ca9e98d11a6ce0424da59cc8794bb32a75ceae06","tid":2034260,"uid":310755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71d8fc5618b0205f375e2128893376b6a5e7d2fd","tid":2034260,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T07:00:11.000Z","msg":"樓主冇邀請鬼妹一齊浸？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:56:04.000Z","msg":"冇膽開口問人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73fd93122d24358360a9e9ac7cee4c13bf004f1c","tid":2034260,"uid":310755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T11:35:27.000Z","msg":"搭唔到巴士只好行過去囉，好彩呢一日係冇行程，但求搵個地方去下放鬆下<br />\n沿路風景唔錯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jcrFrT6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjcrFrT6.jpg&h=d0418418&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行左半個鐘左右終於到<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sPOkrUW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsPOkrUW.jpg&h=6ea28789&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n乜都睇唔到囉屌<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LN7pTCQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLN7pTCQ.jpg&h=296628cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n宣傳用嘅相片明明係咁，呢d都唔知係「理想與現實」定係話佢違反商品及說明條例好<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hkO8ARx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhkO8ARx.jpg&h=81374da9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過點都要喂飽個肚嘅，走咗去農場附設嘅餐廳叫左個烏冬set ，既然呢個係山葵農場照計應該比真正山葵我食嫁嘛？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QqT4TDQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQqT4TDQ.jpg&h=851be5be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我食飽之後就圍住入邊個園區行咗個圈，呢度其中一個最出名嘅景點都係黑澤明嗰個水車，不過嗰日天氣麻麻地冇影到相<br />\n<br />\n行咗一個圈叫做到此一遊之後就去咗食佢嘅山葵雪糕，同行下手信舖頭，係咁以買咗啲山葵零食，然後就去坐巴士返去JR站再坐火車返落去松本<br />\n<br />\n叫得28座大王果然都係流流地"},{"pid":"a00294f08b77136abdc77db24356162439811a76","tid":2034260,"uid":310755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T12:11:39.000Z","msg":"返到松本已經係五點，check in 上房叫做坐低唞吓就準備去浸溫泉<br />\n<br />\n酒店本身係冇溫泉浸，不過可以去同一個集團旗下嘅溫泉旅館 「翔峰」浸佢個日歸溫泉，免費，包埋接送<br />\n<br />\n有得浸咁梗係幾大都上去啦，去reception問佢「Onsen?」，就比左張飛仔我叫我喺酒店大堂等shuttle黎就係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2ywukoe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2ywukoe.jpg&h=cf16cb4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n架shuttle會去三間唔同嘅酒店（都係同一個集團）接晒啲客再上溫泉，車程大約20分鐘<br />\n<br />\n去到溫泉門口落車就會有人收走張飛仔同派毛巾，幾唔錯連自備毛巾都慳返<br />\n<br />\n個溫泉又幾鬼死正，下次如果有旅伴嘅都應該會上嚟住返晚一泊兩食<br />\n<br />\n溫泉官網嘅相<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NYf3pWO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNYf3pWO.png&h=4a3ebebd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ysDo9ou.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FysDo9ou.png&h=68e1768b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n趁冇人偷偷地影一張<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FSku4QN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFSku4QN.jpg&h=b616c23f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n浸完就返番落去松本，浸完溫泉開始有啲肚餓啦，既然黎得長野就咁就食蕎麥麵<br />\n<br />\n打開個tabelog搵到間都有3.5x既蕎麥面舖頭，就喺jr站出邊<br />\n<br />\n叫咗個天婦羅蕎麥面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xDMidOw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxDMidOw.jpg&h=0b5b0c60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你問我好食唔好食我老閪都話好食啦係咪<br />\n<br />\n食飽之後就去便利店買埋宵夜同甜品就番左酒店啦<br />\n<br />\n冇乜特別事做既第二日就咁完左<br />\n<br />\n之後嗰日就真係不得了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qo53pZY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqo53pZY.jpg&h=6d032314&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b26b1ebd2ef2d67575b6ade1ef62bc75eb830bfa","tid":2034260,"uid":8934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T12:34:24.000Z","msg":"長野蕎麥麵好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}